dcterms:description: The FB15k-237 dataset contains knowledge base relation triples and textual mentions of Freebase entity pairs, as used in the work published in (Toutanova and Chen 2015). The knowledge base triples are a subset of the FB15K.
dcterms:title: FB15k-237

dcterms:description: WN18RR is created from WN18, which is a subset of WordNet. WN18RR dataset ensures that the evaluation dataset does not have inverse relation test leakage.
dcterms:title: WN18RR

dcterms:description: FB15k-237-Attr is created by extracting attribute triples of entities in FB15k-237 from FB24k, which includes entity nodes, attribute nodes, and relation types.
dcterms:title: FB15k-237-Attr

dcterms:creator: Y. Lin

dcterms:description: FB24k is built based on Freebase dataset, selecting entities and relations which constitute at least 30 triples, and includes attribute triples.
